text:
Is that everyone's photos?
...Oh, sorry, I didn't mean to peek!

Huh? Oh, don't worry about it.
This is...

Photos of everyone's outfits.
I got a chance to take them.

Wow, it's impressive.
They're all tailored to each person's personality.

But when they come together,
they still look like L'Antica.

I think... Mitsumine is wearing this outfit
because she wants someone's expectations.

So, I want to meet those expectations,
or something like that.

Yeah... I'm sure there's a lot of expectation
for Yuika Mitsumine  of L'Antica to shine.

Haha... Yeah.
...Alright! Let's give it our all again!

Yeah, I'll support you with all I've got
so that Yuika can shine even more.
